    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, offering a driving experience identical to when it first left the dealership. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking a collector-quality vehicle with zero compromises.",
