    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a practical option for anyone needing dependable transport at a lower price point. The exterior shows clear signs of use, including several noticeable scratches, some minor dents on the side panels, and paint fading on the roof. Inside, the cabin is functional but shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. Mechanically, it runs reliably, though it lacks the refinement of a newer model and may require more frequent maintenance. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
      "price": 20500.0,
